title: Dead Weight [DVDRip 2012 great indie zombie movie].avi
description:
An excellent low-budget full-length zombie movie. This is how it's done. Winner of several movie awards. If you're a fan of dystopian, bleak zombie flicks, watch this.

NOT MUCH BLOOD AND GORE, AND ACTUALLY, FEW ZOMBIES.
So if that's all you care about, pass this up. There's plenty of that out there (I've uploaded a few). But you're missing out IMO. 

Click above for IMDb link.
